Privacy Policy for Proofly Mobile

Last updated: 01/17/2025

1. Data Collection
Proofly Mobile collects the following data to provide its services:

Personal Information: Name, email address, account names (e.g., "Personal," "Work").
Images: Photos of receipts uploaded by users.
2. Data Usage
Your data is used solely to deliver app features, such as organizing receipts and categorizing expenses.

3. Data Storage and Security
All data is stored securely on encrypted servers via Firebase. We take measures to protect your data from unauthorized access.

4. Third-Party Services
Proofly Mobile integrates with Firebase for data storage. No additional third parties have access to your information.

5. User Rights
You can request to delete your data at any time by contacting us at: admin@techalphamatrix.com.

6. Policy Updates
We may revise this policy occasionally. Changes will be communicated via the app.
